description: Experience Seaport’s luxury living at a scale few will ever access. 22 Liberty is one of the City’s premier luxury waterfront developments, located right on Boston Harbor. Enter Residence 12G: This 1,177 SqFt southeast corner residence blends architectural drama with intimate tranquility. Light pours through expansive glass walls, illuminating 10.5-foot ceilings above a tuck-in study. This rare 1-bedroom plus study arrangement is found in only 3 homes throughout the building. The ambiance is sculpted: oak underfoot, marble in the sanctuary bath, and a walk-in closet that feels as appointed as a boutique. In the kitchen, high-gloss lacquer cabinetry and elite appliances frame a space made for culinary artistry and quiet mornings on the private terrace. Secure garage parking makes your welcome seamless. 22 Liberty’s Harbor Club offers serene waterfront respite, while concierge attention ensures every moment is anticipated. Don't miss out on securing this rare opportunity!
